rows.label: qst700505_msg0001
rows.name: Hey, Dio!

rows.label: qst700505_msg0002
rows.name:
Your appearance must
mean... could it be...

rows.label: qst700505_msg0003
rows.name:
It's exactly that. Here, the
item you've been waiting for.

rows.label: qst700505_msg0004
rows.name:
Wonderful! This is what
I was looking for!!

rows.label: qst700505_msg0005
rows.name:
With this, I can surely melt her
heart, frozen in thick ice!

rows.label: qst700505_msg0006
rows.name: Thick ice...

rows.label: qst700505_msg0007
rows.name: G-Good luck!

rows.label: qst700505_msg0008
rows.name: Thank you, kind-hearted people!!

rows.label: qst700505_msg0009
rows.name: ...By the way, who are you?

rows.label: qst700505_msg0010
rows.name:
The requested item was difficult
to create, so I had them help me.

rows.label: qst700505_msg0011
rows.name:
What... Then, thank you
many, many times over!

rows.label: qst700505_msg0012
rows.name:
N-No, no. We're just glad
we could be of help.

rows.label: qst700505_msg0013
rows.name: I hope it goes well.

rows.label: qst700505_msg0014
rows.name: No need to worry.

rows.label: qst700505_msg0015
rows.name: No woman can resist me!!

rows.label: qst700505_msg0016
rows.name: Did this person perhaps hit his head?

rows.label: qst700505_msg0017
rows.name:
Unfortunately, he's perfectly
normal. Please don't mind him.

rows.label: qst700505_msg0018
rows.name: Wait for me, Sarah! My destined one!!

rows.label: qst700505_msg0019
rows.name: ...He falls in love a bit easily.

rows.label: qst700505_msg0020
rows.name:
Even so, his attitude of not
fearing difficulty is admirable.

rows.label: qst700505_msg0021
rows.name: ...I almost want to learn from it.
